Qwen ASR Qt
============

This repository contains the Qt tray application source code. Model weights and
backend binaries are not committed to this repository.

Third-party components used or expected at runtime:

- qwen-asr pure C backend: MIT License,
  https://github.com/antirez/qwen-asr
- Qwen3-ASR-0.6B model family: Apache-2.0,
  https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3-ASR-0.6B
- Qt: available under LGPL/commercial licensing, https://www.qt.io/
- KDE Frameworks GlobalAccel: KDE Frameworks licensing applies,
  https://invent.kde.org/frameworks/kglobalaccel

If a release artifact bundles qwen_asr_server or other third-party binaries, the
release must include the corresponding license texts and notices.
